{
  "message": "\ud83c\udf31 Add dependabot + standard CI workflows (#8)\n\n* \ud83c\udf31 Add dependabot configuration\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* \ud83c\udf31 Add standard CI workflows\n\nAdds signed-commits check, typo check, link check, non-main gatekeeper,\nstale/unstale management, and Prow integration.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "a27a1e48391f676a6b7bf6f51cd90cdeb187389e",
      "filename": ".github/dependabot.yml",
      "status": "added",
      "additions": 13,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 13,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/blob/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fdependabot.yml",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/raw/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fdependabot.yml",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/contents/.github%2Fdependabot.yml?ref=e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@\n+version: 2\n+updates:\n+\n+  # GitHub Actions dependencies\n+  - package-ecosystem: \"github-actions\"\n+    directory: \"/\"\n+    schedule:\n+      interval: \"weekly\"\n+    labels:\n+      - \"dependencies\"\n+      - \"release-note-none\"\n+    commit-message:\n+      prefix: \"deps(actions)\""
    },
    {
      "sha": "72be96d518aae1ba4e8b673924a8d7e70e0984e4",
      "filename": ".github/workflows/check-typos.yaml",
      "status": "added",
      "additions": 8,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 8,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/blob/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fcheck-typos.yaml",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/raw/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fcheck-typos.yaml",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/contents/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fcheck-typos.yaml?ref=e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+name: Check Typos\n+on:\n+  pull_request:\n+  push:\n+\n+jobs:\n+  typos:\n+    uses: llm-d/llm-d-infra/.github/workflows/reusable-typos.yml@main"
    },
    {
      "sha": "2b374bf714a29bced1184a0fe51a22f601ebb621",
      "filename": ".github/workflows/ci-signed-commits.yaml",
      "status": "added",
      "additions": 9,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 9,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/blob/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fci-signed-commits.yaml",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/raw/e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fci-signed-commits.yaml",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/llm-d-incubation/llm-d-ci/contents/.github%2Fworkflows%2Fci-signed-commits.yaml?ref=e39b19d123b0d7726fe14289c395d5b0e27589ad",
      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+name: Check Signed Commits\n+on: pull_request_target\n+\n+jobs:\n+  signed-commits:\n+    uses: llm-d/llm-d-infra/.github/workflows/reusable-signed-commits.yml@main\n+    permissions:\n+      contents: read\n+      pull-requests: write"
    },
    {
